Package com.vrm.client

Class LeaseManager

java.lang.Object
com.vrm.client.LeaseManager
public class LeaseManager extends Object
Responsible for managing vehicle leases within a fleet. Allows for creation, retrieval, and removal of leases, as well as tracking leases by client.

    • createLease

      public int createLease(Client client, String plateNumber)
      Creates a new lease for a vehicle and associates it with a client. Updates the vehicle's leased status.
      Parameters:
      client - The client leasing the vehicle.
      plateNumber - The license plate number of the vehicle to lease.
      Returns:
      0 if successful, 1 if vehicle is null, 2 if vehicle is already leased, 3 if lease array is full, 4 if vehicle lease toggle fails.

    • getLastLeaseID

    • removeLease

      public int removeLease(int iD)
      Removes a lease by its ID. Terminated leases set vehicle to not leased.
      Parameters:
      iD - The ID of the lease to remove.
      Returns:
      0 if successful, 1 if no leases exist, 2 if lease ID not found.
